name: Neon union
description: I want to dedicate this series of works to gossip and its redisseminators. It is so common for women to be the main messengers of gossip. I don’t want to hide, I like to gossip and I do it tastefully. For example, with a delicious cocktail, in a pleasant atmosphere and with people close to me. But there’s never anything wrong with this conversation. I just blow off steam with my girlfriends and share news. But gossipers aren’t always as harmless as they seem. And in my series «Neon Union» I want to tell you about types of gossip , and you decide for yourself, maybe you are one of them?
